These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
Transport: van, tram, bike
1. Transport:bike is on the far left or far right##3
2. Transport:tram is on the left of Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Transport   | van | tram | bike |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
Job: paramedic, nurse, security-guard
1. Job:nurse is on the far left or far right##3
2. Job:security-guard is in the middle##1
3. Job:security-guard is on the right of Job:paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Job   | paramedic | security-guard | nurse |

